snippet.title: Tiny Thor - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Tiny Thor on: http://store.steampowered.com/app/541310/

Tiny Thor – Become a HeroSlip into the role of the legendary Thunder God Thor. Battle throngs of enemies with your hammer, collect coins and jewels, solve switch puzzles and explore intricate mazes. Destroy your surroundings with your hammer to battle your way to the exit or to bonus caves.

Games reviews and download: http://download.online-games.co/
